{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.1","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:1","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.009.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">J\u00e9hu, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-16: cf. 2 R 9:6-9. 1 R 21:21-29. (J\u00e9 35.) Ps 119:113.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Il y avait dans Samarie soixante-dix fils d\u2019Achab. J\u00e9hu \u00e9crivit des lettres qu\u2019il envoya \u00e0 Samarie aux chefs de Jizreel, aux anciens, et aux gouverneurs des enfants d\u2019Achab. Il y \u00e9tait dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.2","name":"2 Rois 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.9.37","name":"2 Rois 9:37","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.9.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.2","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:2","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Maintenant, quand cette lettre vous sera parvenue, puisque vous avez avec vous les fils de votre ma\u00eetre, avec vous les chars et les chevaux, une ville forte et les armes,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.3","name":"2 Rois 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.1","name":"2 Rois 10:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.3","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:3","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>voyez lequel des fils de votre ma\u00eetre est le meilleur et convient le mieux, mettez-le sur le tr\u00f4ne de son p\u00e8re, et combattez pour la maison de votre ma\u00eetre!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.4","name":"2 Rois 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.2","name":"2 Rois 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.4","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:4","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Ils eurent une tr\u00e8s grande peur, et ils dirent: Voici, deux rois n\u2019ont pu lui r\u00e9sister; comment r\u00e9sisterions-nous?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.5","name":"2 Rois 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.3","name":"2 Rois 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.5","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:5","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Et le chef de la maison, le chef de la ville, les anciens, et les gouverneurs des enfants, envoy\u00e8rent dire \u00e0 J\u00e9hu: Nous sommes tes serviteurs, et nous ferons tout ce que tu nous diras; nous n\u2019\u00e9tablirons personne roi, fais ce qui te semble bon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.6","name":"2 Rois 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.4","name":"2 Rois 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.6","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:6","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>J\u00e9hu leur \u00e9crivit une seconde lettre o\u00f9 il \u00e9tait dit: Si vous \u00eates \u00e0 moi et si vous ob\u00e9issez \u00e0 ma voix, prenez les t\u00eates de ces hommes, fils de votre ma\u00eetre, et venez aupr\u00e8s de moi demain \u00e0 cette heure, \u00e0 Jizreel. Or les soixante-dix fils du roi \u00e9taient chez les grands de la ville, qui les \u00e9levaient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.7","name":"2 Rois 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.5","name":"2 Rois 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.7","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:7","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Quand la lettre leur fut parvenue, ils prirent les fils du roi, et ils \u00e9gorg\u00e8rent ces soixante-dix hommes; puis ils mirent leurs t\u00eates dans des corbeilles, et les envoy\u00e8rent \u00e0 J\u00e9hu, \u00e0 Jizreel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.8","name":"2 Rois 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.6","name":"2 Rois 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.8","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:8","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Le messager vint l\u2019en informer, en disant: Ils ont apport\u00e9 les t\u00eates des fils du roi. Et il dit: Mettez-les en deux tas \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la porte, jusqu\u2019au matin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.9","name":"2 Rois 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.7","name":"2 Rois 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.9","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:9","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Le matin, il sortit; et se pr\u00e9sentant \u00e0 tout le peuple, il dit: Vous \u00eates justes! Voici, moi, j\u2019ai conspir\u00e9 contre mon ma\u00eetre et je l\u2019ai tu\u00e9; mais qui a frapp\u00e9 tous ceux-ci?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.10","name":"2 Rois 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.8","name":"2 Rois 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.10","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:10","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Sachez donc qu\u2019il ne tombera rien \u00e0 terre de la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, de la parole que l\u2019\u00c9ternel a prononc\u00e9e contre la maison d\u2019Achab; l\u2019\u00c9ternel accomplit ce qu\u2019il a d\u00e9clar\u00e9 par son serviteur \u00c9lie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.11","name":"2 Rois 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.9","name":"2 Rois 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.11","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:11","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et J\u00e9hu frappa tous ceux qui restaient de la maison d\u2019Achab \u00e0 Jizreel, tous ses grands, ses familiers et ses ministres, sans en laisser \u00e9chapper un seul.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.12","name":"2 Rois 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.10","name":"2 Rois 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.12","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:12","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Puis il se leva, et partit pour aller \u00e0 Samarie. Arriv\u00e9 \u00e0 une maison de r\u00e9union des bergers, sur le chemin,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.13","name":"2 Rois 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.11","name":"2 Rois 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.13","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:13","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>J\u00e9hu trouva les fr\u00e8res d\u2019Achazia, roi de Juda, et il dit: Qui \u00eates-vous? Ils r\u00e9pondirent: Nous sommes les fr\u00e8res d\u2019Achazia, et nous descendons pour saluer les fils du roi et les fils de la reine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.14","name":"2 Rois 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.12","name":"2 Rois 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.14","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:14","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>J\u00e9hu dit: Saisissez-les vivants. Et ils les saisirent vivants, et les \u00e9gorg\u00e8rent au nombre de quarante-deux, \u00e0 la citerne de la maison de r\u00e9union; J\u00e9hu n\u2019en laissa \u00e9chapper aucun.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.15","name":"2 Rois 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.13","name":"2 Rois 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.15","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:15","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>\u00c9tant parti de l\u00e0, il rencontra Jonadab, fils de R\u00e9cab, qui venait au-devant de lui. Il le salua, et lui dit: Ton c\u0153ur est-il sinc\u00e8re, comme mon c\u0153ur l\u2019est envers le tien? Et Jonadab r\u00e9pondit: Il l\u2019est. S\u2019il l\u2019est, r\u00e9pliqua J\u00e9hu, donne-moi ta main. Jonadab lui donna la main. Et J\u00e9hu le fit monter aupr\u00e8s de lui dans son char,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.16","name":"2 Rois 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.14","name":"2 Rois 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.16","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:16","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>et dit: Viens avec moi, et tu verras mon z\u00e8le pour l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Il l\u2019emmena ainsi dans son char.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.17","name":"2 Rois 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.15","name":"2 Rois 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.17","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:17","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.018,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La famille d\u2019Achab et les proph\u00e8tes de Baal extermin\u00e9s<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 17-27: cf. (1 R 18:18-40; 19:16-18. De 13.) Ps 92:10. J\u00e9 48:10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Lorsque J\u00e9hu fut arriv\u00e9 \u00e0 Samarie, il frappa tous ceux qui restaient d\u2019Achab \u00e0 Samarie, et il les d\u00e9truisit enti\u00e8rement, selon la parole que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait dite \u00e0 \u00c9lie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.18","name":"2 Rois 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.16","name":"2 Rois 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.18","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:18","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Puis il assembla tout le peuple, et leur dit: Achab a peu servi Baal, J\u00e9hu le servira beaucoup.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.19","name":"2 Rois 10:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.17","name":"2 Rois 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.19","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:19","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Maintenant convoquez aupr\u00e8s de moi tous les proph\u00e8tes de Baal, tous ses serviteurs et tous ses pr\u00eatres, sans qu\u2019il en manque un seul, car je veux offrir un grand sacrifice \u00e0 Baal: quiconque manquera ne vivra pas. J\u00e9hu agissait avec ruse, pour faire p\u00e9rir les serviteurs de Baal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.20","name":"2 Rois 10:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.18","name":"2 Rois 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.20","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:20","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Il dit: Publiez une f\u00eate en l\u2019honneur de Baal. Et ils la publi\u00e8rent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.21","name":"2 Rois 10:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.19","name":"2 Rois 10:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.21","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:21","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Il envoya des messagers dans tout Isra\u00ebl; et tous les serviteurs de Baal arriv\u00e8rent, il n\u2019y en eut pas un qui ne v\u00eent; ils entr\u00e8rent dans la maison de Baal, et la maison de Baal fut remplie d\u2019un bout \u00e0 l\u2019autre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.22","name":"2 Rois 10:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.20","name":"2 Rois 10:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.22","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:22","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>J\u00e9hu dit \u00e0 celui qui avait la garde du vestiaire: Sors des v\u00eatements pour tous les serviteurs de Baal. Et cet homme sortit des v\u00eatements pour eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.23","name":"2 Rois 10:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.21","name":"2 Rois 10:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.23","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:23","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Alors J\u00e9hu vint \u00e0 la maison de Baal avec Jonadab, fils de R\u00e9cab, et il dit aux serviteurs de Baal: Cherchez et regardez, afin qu\u2019il n\u2019y ait pas ici des serviteurs de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, mais qu\u2019il y ait seulement des serviteurs de Baal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.24","name":"2 Rois 10:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.22","name":"2 Rois 10:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.24","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:24","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Et ils entr\u00e8rent pour offrir des sacrifices et des holocaustes. J\u00e9hu avait plac\u00e9 dehors quatre-vingts hommes, en leur disant: Celui qui laissera \u00e9chapper quelqu\u2019un des hommes que je remets entre vos mains, sa vie r\u00e9pondra de la sienne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.25","name":"2 Rois 10:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.23","name":"2 Rois 10:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.25","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:25","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019on eut achev\u00e9 d\u2019offrir les holocaustes, J\u00e9hu dit aux coureurs et aux officiers: Entrez, frappez-les, que pas un ne sorte. Et ils les frapp\u00e8rent du tranchant de l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e. Les coureurs et les officiers les jet\u00e8rent l\u00e0, et ils all\u00e8rent jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la ville de la maison de Baal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.26","name":"2 Rois 10:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.24","name":"2 Rois 10:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.26","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:26","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Ils tir\u00e8rent dehors les statues de la maison de Baal, et les br\u00fbl\u00e8rent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.27","name":"2 Rois 10:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.25","name":"2 Rois 10:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.27","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:27","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Ils renvers\u00e8rent la statue de Baal, ils renvers\u00e8rent aussi la maison de Baal, et ils en firent un cloaque, qui a subsist\u00e9 jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.28","name":"2 Rois 10:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.26","name":"2 Rois 10:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.28","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:28","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.029,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 28-36: cf. 1 S 15:18-23. (2 R 17:21-23. Am 1:3-4.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>J\u00e9hu extermina Baal du milieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.29","name":"2 Rois 10:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.27","name":"2 Rois 10:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.29","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:29","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>mais il ne se d\u00e9tourna point des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s de J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath, qui avait fait p\u00e9cher Isra\u00ebl, il n\u2019abandonna point les veaux d\u2019or qui \u00e9taient \u00e0 B\u00e9thel et \u00e0 Dan.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.30","name":"2 Rois 10:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.28","name":"2 Rois 10:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.30","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:30","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 J\u00e9hu: Parce que tu as bien ex\u00e9cut\u00e9 ce qui \u00e9tait droit \u00e0 mes yeux, et que tu as fait \u00e0 la maison d\u2019Achab tout ce qui \u00e9tait conforme \u00e0 ma volont\u00e9, tes fils jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la quatri\u00e8me g\u00e9n\u00e9ration seront assis sur le tr\u00f4ne d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.31","name":"2 Rois 10:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.29","name":"2 Rois 10:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.31","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:31","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Toutefois J\u00e9hu ne prit point garde \u00e0 marcher de tout son c\u0153ur dans la loi de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl; il ne se d\u00e9tourna point des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s que J\u00e9roboam avait fait commettre \u00e0 Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.32","name":"2 Rois 10:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.30","name":"2 Rois 10:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.32","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:32","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Dans ce temps-l\u00e0, l\u2019\u00c9ternel commen\u00e7a \u00e0 entamer le territoire d\u2019Isra\u00ebl; et Haza\u00ebl les battit sur toute la fronti\u00e8re d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.33","name":"2 Rois 10:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.31","name":"2 Rois 10:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.33","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:33","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Depuis le Jourdain, vers le soleil levant, il battit tout le pays de Galaad, les Gadites, les Rub\u00e9nites et les Manassites, depuis Aro\u00ebr sur le torrent de l\u2019Arnon jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Galaad et \u00e0 Basan.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.34","name":"2 Rois 10:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.32","name":"2 Rois 10:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.34","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:34","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Le reste des actions de J\u00e9hu, tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, et tous ses exploits, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.35","name":"2 Rois 10:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.33","name":"2 Rois 10:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.35","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:35","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>J\u00e9hu se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, et on l\u2019enterra \u00e0 Samarie. Et Joachaz, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.36","name":"2 Rois 10:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.34","name":"2 Rois 10:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.36","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 10:36","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.010.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.011.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.10.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>J\u00e9hu avait r\u00e9gn\u00e9 vingt-huit ans sur Isra\u00ebl \u00e0 Samarie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10","name":"2 Rois 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.11.1","name":"2 Rois 11:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.11.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.35","name":"2 Rois 10:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.10.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb3a54e51.99090648');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb3a54e51.99090648\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb3a54e51.99090648","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb3a54e51.99090648'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb3a54e51.99090648\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}